title: Couple With Heart Man Man Dark Skin Tone Medium Dark Skin Tone
description: Represents a romantic couple composed of two men, with one having a dark skin tone and the other a medium-dark skin tone, symbolizing love and partnership.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, the couple with heart emoji featuring two men with dark and medium-dark skin tones radiates warmth and connection. Apple's signature glossy 3D shading and smooth gradients create a visually appealing representation of their bond, with the heart glowing vibrantly between them. This emoji is a powerful symbol of love, unity, and romantic partnership, celebrated with Apple's inclusive design approach.
